As a customer
So that I can check if I want to order something
I would like to see a list of dishes with prices

in irb:
create new takeaway object
  'takeaway = Takeaway.new'
access the menu
  'takeaway.read_menu'

---------------------------------------------------------

As a customer
So that I can order the meal I want
I would like to be able to select some number of several available dishes

in irb:
create new takeaway object
  'takeaway = Takeaway.new'
access the menu
  'takeaway.read_menu'
select an item to add to basket
  'takeaway.order("Pepperoni)'
select another item to add to basket
  'takeaway.order("Margherita")'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

As a customer
So that I can verify that my order is correct
I would like to check that the total I have been given matches the sum of the various dishes in my order

in irb:
create new takeaway object
  'takeaway = Takeaway.new'
access the menu
  'takeaway.read_menu'
select an item to add to basket
  'takeaway.order("Pepperoni)'
select another item to add to basket
  'takeaway.order("Margherita")'
view basket summary to see my order and the cost
  'takeaway.basket_summary'